      "content": "i get that, but my doctor isn't really available right now and the pain is getting annoying. it's not like my kidney issues are super advanced or anything, just stage 2. wouldn't a standard dose of ibuprofen be fine for a simple headache? i dont want to have to wait until monday to feel better.",
